metadata.name: Certified Fake XCOPY
metadata.description: Waiting for MAXPAIN reveal is a valid pain point. But having nothing around you but fake frenz is even more painful. . . and now you're about to mint a CERTIFIED FAKE COPY of the meme card: Authentic Summer. And later on will have this hidden in your wallet. What can be more painful than this? All pepe followers join the sad club and meet new fake frenz. If we're mocking the pain enough maybe we can send this fakememe card to fakememes series 0? Then things might get a little lighter. hmmmmmmmm.
